subject: NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Handed No. 12 seeds, but sent to the same site to open the N.C.A.A. tournament, Oregon and California provided back-to-back upsets of fifth-seeded opponents to lift the Pacific-12 Conference’s reputation.
